  "title": "Sales Engineer[ Own car/ West/Water Jetting & Industrial Cleaning division]",
  "description": "<p>The role is to market a full range of Professional &amp; Industrial Cleaning equipment, and accessories &amp; tools, to corporate customers, with an emphasis in oil and gas sectors.</p>\n<p>Job Scope</p>\n<p>- serve existing assigned accounts and prospect potential new customers</p>\n<p>- learn &amp; familiarise our products well, understand users’ needs, and so be able to offer solutions and assistance to meet their requirements</p>\n<p>- perform hands-on product demonstrations, as well as occasionally conduct presentations to mid-size audiences including management levels</p>\n<p>Job requirement</p>\n<p>· be customer and sales oriented</p>\n<p>· possess a strong sense of self-discipline, integrity &amp; initiative; work well independently, yet be a good team player</p>\n<p>· own basic IT skills in document, presentation &amp; spreadsheet softwares; WhatsApp and other common apps</p>\n<p>· have earned a Polytechnic Diploma or equivalent; preferably in a business associated or engineering related field …..</p>\n<p>· and/or be experienced in corporate/industrial sales, especially in the oil and gas setting</p>\n<p>· hold a Class 3 driving license and own a car</p>",
